<!-- =========================================================================================
    File Name: FeatherIcon.vue
    Description: Feather icon component. Creates feather icon based on 'icon' prop
    Component Name: FeatherIcon
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Item Name: Vuexy - Vuejs, HTML & Laravel Admin Dashboard Template
      Author: Pixinvent
    Author URL: http://www.themeforest.net/user/pixinvent
========================================================================================== -->

<script>
import * as icons from "vue-feather-icons";

export default {
  functional: true,
  name: "feather-icon",
  props: {
    icon: { required: true },
    svgClasses: { type: [String, Object, Array], default: "" },
    badge: {},
  },
  render(h, { props, data }) {
    // Add feather classes
    data.staticClass
      ? (data.staticClass = `${data.staticClass} feather-icon select-none relative`)
      : (data.staticClass = "feather-icon select-none relative");

    const svg = h(icons[props.icon], { class: props.svgClasses });
    const badgeEl = h(
      "span",
      {
        class:
          "feather-icon-badge bg-primary text-white h-5 w-5 absolute rounded-full text-xs flex items-center justify-center",
        style: "top: -7px; right: -5px",
      },
      [props.badge]
    );
    const children = [svg];
    if (props.badge) children.push(badgeEl);
    return h("span", data, children);
  },
};
</script>

<style lang="scss">
@import "@/assets/utils/vuexy/components/featherIcon.scss";
</style>
